<li><a id="org02f8744"></a>What does Macbeth tell them to do?<br />
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><a id="orgcff3fdc"></a>Macbeth tells them to kill Banquo and Fleance tonight before supper while he is off and away riding his horse. He tells them to make sure the deed is done and to end it here once and for all.<br /></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
